rows.details: Dialogflow ES integration, project versioning, auto-panning, new built-in entities and more [is now available](https://www.notion.so/voiceflow/Voiceflow-Changelog-b5e32e269b204106b5b51014cd049346#026b9a50a25449d1b9132528eb1f9ff7)

A new project navigation launched today. [Take a tour!](https://www.notion.so/voiceflow/Voiceflow-Changelog-b5e32e269b204106b5b51014cd049346#026b9a50a25449d1b9132528eb1f9ff7)

Updates to the Speak Step, Choice Step, Comments [and more](https://www.notion.so/voiceflow/Voiceflow-Changelog-b5e32e269b204106b5b51014cd049346#396ea476ffb74febb767758f7adbf6b8)
Functionality and design improvements to the Prototype Test Tool [are out now](https://www.notion.so/voiceflow/Voiceflow-Changelog-b5e32e269b204106b5b51014cd049346#396ea476ffb74febb767758f7adbf6b8)
More options for Canvas Navigation have been [introduced](https://www.notion.so/voiceflow/Voiceflow-Changelog-b5e32e269b204106b5b51014cd049346#396ea476ffb74febb767758f7adbf6b8)
